  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a bento box over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the lamb shoulder and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the chicken broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Transfer the bento box to the oven and braise the lamb for 2 hours, or until tender.",
    "Stir in the parsley and lemon juice, and serve warm.",
    "Serve the tagine over couscous or with some crusty bread.",
    "Adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Garnish with additional parsley if desired."
